sufian.video.server

Class RTSPResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • sufian.video.server.RTSPResponse

  • public class RTSPResponse
extends Object
    A class for creating responses to RTSP requests from client.

    See details on RTSP responses in RFC 2326 section 7.

    Author:
    Sufian Latif
